950
00:46:25,470 --> 00:46:26,870
I won't be jealous of you.

951
00:46:28,980 --> 00:46:29,700
Tianhe.

952
00:46:30,030 --> 00:46:31,420
You even get jealous

953
00:46:31,440 --> 00:46:33,480
