954
00:46:35,670 --> 00:46:36,790
Tianhe, listen up.

955
00:46:37,220 --> 00:46:38,650
Now that we've been through this,

956
00:46:38,650 --> 00:46:40,250
Ziying is our older brother.

957
00:46:40,500 --> 00:46:42,720
